<author>Patrick J . RAKOTO RAMIARANTSOA</author>
<title>'NDRETO IZAHAY ASAFA82</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 'Ndreto 'zahay Tompo ô!
 Hitsaoka ny Anaranao
 Ho Anao irery anie mandrakizay
 Ny voninahitra
 Izao rehetra izao
 Mihoby Anao Tompo ô!</lyrics>
</song>